      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "有一个数列：一、一、二、五、十四、四十二。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "它叫卡特兰数，看似普通，却藏在许多问题的答案里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "括号、二叉树、多边形，答案居然都是同一串数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "paren",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "paren-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/paren-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "先看括号：n 对括号能排出多少种合法写法？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "paren",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "paren-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/paren-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "合法意味着任何前缀里，右括号都不多于左括号。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "paren",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "paren-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/paren-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "三对括号有五种，这正好是卡特兰数 C 三。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-1",
      "filename": "tree-tree-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "再看二叉树：n 个内部节点能长出多少种不同形态？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-2",
      "filename": "tree-tree-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "每一种合法括号，都对应唯一一棵二叉树的形状。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-3",
      "filename": "tree-tree-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "于是它们的数目完全相同，都是卡特兰数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "poly",
      "line_id": "poly-1",
      "filename": "poly-poly-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/poly-poly-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "第三个面孔：把凸多边形用不相交的对角线切成三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "poly",
      "line_id": "poly-2",
      "filename": "poly-poly-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/poly-poly-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "一个 n 加二 边形的剖分方案数，恰好是 C n。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "poly",
      "line_id": "poly-3",
      "filename": "poly-poly-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/poly-poly-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.69,
      "size": 43056,
      "text": "同一个递推 C n 加一 等于各项两两相乘再求和，在背后统一了这一切。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "选择不同的 n，看这个数如何随规模迅速增长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "切换视角，同一个 C n 会以括号、树或多边形出现。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "卡特兰数由简单递推生成，也有闭式 C 二n 取 n 再除以 n 加一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catalan-numbers/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "它把括号、二叉树、三角剖分等问题串成一家。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catalan-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
